## 22. Generate Parentheses (Medium)

<p>
Given <i>n</i> pairs of parentheses, write a function to generate all combinations of well-formed parentheses.
</p>

<p>
For example, given <i>n</i> = 3, a solution set is:
</p>
<pre>
[
  "((()))",
  "(()())",
  "(())()",
  "()(())",
  "()()()"
]
</pre>
